      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHOS DELIGHT NZ (5) should find this easier than recent attempts. Far from disgraced after racing parked last week and had kicked off in Australia with back-to-back wins here in February. Finds the right race to return to the winners' list. BIGGER THE BETTOR NZ (1) produced a better performance when second up last time out, finishing 3.4m away in third at this circuit and distance. Has won third-up before so will strip fitter again and should enjoy an economical run from the ace draw. OZZIE PUNTA (8) is racing well with a win and two seconds from his last three starts here. Draws on the back row but won from there last month so has to come into calculations. MANILA PLAYBOY (6) hasn't raced for four-and-a-half months but is a four-time fresh winner so can open this campaign with a positive effort.",
